    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest3607215615440725633.title":"&e&l传说—&6凋零之眼",
    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest3755364829256556249.description1":"进入末地，并击杀凶残的&d<shake>末影龙！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest3755364829256556249.reward.8285918206934966551.title":"&e解锁头衔：&r虚空之主",
    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest3755364829256556249.subtitle":"解锁末地",
    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest3755364829256556249.task.2534550615252848297.title":"&d击杀末影龙",
    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest3755364829256556249.title":"&d<shake>末地",
    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest4161195811415355734.description1":"&e虚空之花&r是一个极其危险的敌人。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest4161195811415355734.description2":"这株疯狂生长的巨型植物一直在吸取地下所有的虚空能量，现在已经变得无比庞大！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest4161195811415355734.description3":"据说&e蔓延之眼&r蕴含着他们的生命精华，甚至死后还能再生！而且我们可算老相识啦！我认识他的时候他还在地里是个小苗苗呢！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest4161195811415355734.description4":"&6提示：&r你可以在&d基岩&r附近找到&e虚空之花&r。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest4161195811415355734.description5":"&6☠难度：&4&l困难",
    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest4161195811415355734.image0":"{image:modpack:textures/2025-03-14_00.41.44.png width:200 height:100 align:center}",
    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest4161195811415355734.reward.3983148001029080290.title":"&e解锁头衔：&r根蔓克星",
    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest4161195811415355734.subtitle":"&a&o主世界阶段",
    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest4161195811415355734.title":"&e&l传说—&6蔓延之眼",
    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest4404459266648913869.description1":"为了打开通往&e末地&r的传送门，你需要寻找&l十二&r件（只需要12件）强大的物品……",
    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest4404459266648913869.description2":"这些物品被称为&6“传说之眼”",
    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest4404459266648913869.description3":"找到它们&o可不是件容易的事！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest4404459266648913869.description4":"据说每只眼睛都受到&4&o强大的敌人保护，他们&r都会坚决保护各自的眼睛！勇往直前，把它们全部集齐吧，为了&m我！&r为了我们！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest4404459266648913869.description5":"你每收集到一颗&6传说之眼&r，就会在此Boss图鉴中解锁一个&d水晶头骨&r来展示你的进度！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest4404459266648913869.description6":"&2&o祝你好运！—QM",
    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest4404459266648913869.image0":"{image:modpack:textures/end_portal.png width:200 height:110 align:1 fit:true}",
    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest4404459266648913869.subtitle":"了解传说之眼！",
