    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest4404459266648913869.title":"&6传说之眼！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest440880643128562747.description1":"有小概率在下界找到&e下界铁掌&r！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest440880643128562747.description2":"找到并消灭它！务必保持警惕，眼观六路……",
    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest440880643128562747.description3":"&o&7嗯，这个方块看起来有点可疑！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest440880643128562747.description4":"&6☠难度：&3&l中等",
