    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest4531714763290880117.description1":"传说&e远古之眼&r由&e远古遗魂&r守护",
    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest4531714763290880117.description2":"我会送你去沙漠寻找它！",
    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest4531714763290880117.description3":"我不能自己去，因为&o我不喜欢沙子。&r它又粗又硬又烦人，而且到处都是。",
    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest4531714763290880117.description4":"&e小窍门：&r注意可疑的沙子！",
