    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest7137369629242663414.subtitle":"归还丢失的物品",
    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest7160324107286133209.description1":"数千年前，&e迷离之眼&r是在&d下界灵魂熔炉&r中锻造的……我想知道它在哪里？又是谁弄丢了它？",
    "ftbquests.chapter.bosses.quest7160324107286133209.description2":"&6☠难度：&4&l困难",
